author: joyce
msg: - Init now uses add_datasets to add the datasets to the Evaluation.
- add_datasets now iterates over the List of Datasets and passes each to
add_dataset. This allows us to more easily check that each dataset is
an instance of the Dataset class.
- Add check to add_dataset to ensure that a dataset is an instance of
the Dataset class. Otherwise, raise a ValueError.
